      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "text": "Claude Sonnet: ~5x more expensive for the same ranking quality. OpenAI GPT-4o-mini: similar price but harsher on\nIndian-English phrasing.\nHaiku wins: ~$0.001 per run, ~2 seconds, smart enough for 'which of these stories match the topic'.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 12,
      "originalText": "Claude Sonnet: ~5x more expensive for the same ranking quality. OpenAI GPT-4o-mini: similar price but harsher on\nIndian-English phrasing.\nHaiku wins: ~$0.001 per run, ~2 seconds, smart enough for 'which of these stories match the topic'.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": "el_IIdQIAhp4n0KGl",
      "autoResize": false
    },
