      "fontFamily": 2,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "text": "Raw ffmpeg: can't do animated motion text. CapCut API: same input gives you a different video each time (not\nreliable). After Effects: no real automation API.\nRemotion wins: code-driven, same input always gives the same output, lives in git, I already use it in another\nproject so scenes are reusable.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 12,
      "originalText": "Raw ffmpeg: can't do animated motion text. CapCut API: same input gives you a different video each time (not\nreliable). After Effects: no real automation API.\nRemotion wins: code-driven, same input always gives the same output, lives in git, I already use it in another\nproject so scenes are reusable.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": "el_qtpasWt7eI9im2",
      "autoResize": false
    },
