      "fontFamily": 2,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "text": "Redis / Postgres: real databases, but overkill for a solo project. n8n's built-in memory: only remembers things\nper-workflow, NOT across workflows - broke our setup. Learned that the hard way.\nFlat JSON files win: simplest thing that works. Both workflows read / write the same folder. Easy to debug with a\ntext editor.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 12,
      "originalText": "Redis / Postgres: real databases, but overkill for a solo project. n8n's built-in memory: only remembers things\nper-workflow, NOT across workflows - broke our setup. Learned that the hard way.\nFlat JSON files win: simplest thing that works. Both workflows read / write the same folder. Easy to debug with a\ntext editor.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": "el_nzm4kjZNvp5zzP",
      "autoResize": false
    },
