      "fontFamily": 2,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "text": "Runs every minute in the background. If the render engine died, it\nrestarts. If the bot's public URL drifted (cloudflared rotates it\non restart), it reconnects. Zero-touch recovery.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "originalText": "Runs every minute in the background. If the render engine died, it\nrestarts. If the bot's public URL drifted (cloudflared rotates it\non restart), it reconnects. Zero-touch recovery.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": null,
      "autoResize": false
    },
