      "seed": 800699537,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 389229337,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777146527408,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "fontSize": 17,
      "text": "AI is often confident and wrong.  So I draft three reel options up front and let the human pick one.\nCost of drafting three options  ~= $0.12 total.  Cost of the wrong reel going out to an audience  = brand damage.\nOne approval tap  = tiny cost, massive upside.  Same pattern I would use for any customer-facing AI content flow.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "originalText": "AI is often confident and wrong.  So I draft three reel options up front and let the human pick one.\nCost of drafting three options  ~= $0.12 total.  Cost of the wrong reel going out to an audience  = brand damage.\nOne approval tap  = tiny cost, massive upside.  Same pattern I would use for any customer-facing AI content flow.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": null,
      "autoResize": false
    },
