      "fontSize": 15,
      "text": "Add a job queue (so requests line up instead of colliding) and\nrent render servers on-demand from the cloud. Goes from 1 user to\n50+ users simultaneously without rewriting the core flow.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "originalText": "Add a job queue (so requests line up instead of colliding) and\nrent render servers on-demand from the cloud. Goes from 1 user to\n50+ users simultaneously without rewriting the core flow.",
